543
00:29:58,300 --> 00:30:00,740
- No?
- If you have something to say,

544
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:03,070
I can call her and have her come by.

545
00:30:03,110 --> 00:30:06,080
No, it's nothing urgent,
so don't concern yourself with it.

546
00:30:06,540 --> 00:30:07,610
Understood, sir.

547
00:30:14,250 --> 00:30:16,820
Who on earth said
something like that?

548
00:30:16,950 --> 00:30:20,720
